HEADWORD: Horrify
<hw>Hor"ri*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Horrified</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
